OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775981091
OL,3,CFurther motorway closures due to
OL,4,Cprotests as fuel stations run dry
OL,6,FGarda introduced "exceptional"
OL,7,Fmeasures as fuel protests which have
OL,8,Fstrangled the distribution of fuel
OL,9,Faround the country rumbled into a
OL,10,Ffifth consecutive day.
OL,12,FThe Irish Government is to re-enter
OL,13,Ftalks on Saturday aimed at defusing
OL,14,Fthe protests, which have involved
OL,15,Fblockades at key fuel distribution
OL,16,Fsites, as the prospect of most filling
OL,17,Fstations running out of fuel by Monday
OL,18,Fwas raised by an industry
OL,19,Frepresentative.
OL,26,@nD@ROUnD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
