CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775981091
OL,3,CFurther motorway closures due to
OL,4,Cprotests as fuel stations run dry
OL,6,FIt comes after a crunch meeting on
OL,7,FFriday failed to end with concrete
OL,8,Fproposals.
OL,10,FAn Garda Siochana internally declared
OL,11,Fan "exceptional event", allowing it to
OL,12,Fdesignate every member available for
OL,13,Fduty over the weekend.
OL,15,FAbout 600 of the 1,500 filling
OL,16,Fstations around the Republic of
OL,17,FIreland have run dry, according to
OL,18,FFuels for Ireland chief executive
OL,19,FKevin McPartlan.
OL,26,@sD@DOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775981091
OL,3,CFurther motorway closures due to
OL,4,Cprotests as fuel stations run dry
OL,6,FHe said he expected the number "will
OL,7,Fgrow quite dramatically" if ongoing
OL,8,Fblockades of fuel depots remain in
OL,9,Fplace.
OL,11,FDespite this, Health Minister Jennifer
OL,12,FCarroll MacNeill told the Irish
OL,13,FMedical Organisation AGM in Co Kerry
OL,14,Fon Saturday that "all of our
OL,15,Fambulances have been refuelled
OL,16,Fsuccessfully".
OL,18,FElsewhere, Rosslare Europort is
OL,19,Fexpected to hit capacity by Sunday
OL,20,Fevening or Monday morning.
OL,26,@nD@`OUoD@XO]vD@ROUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
