OL,3,CFurther motorway closures due to
OL,4,Cprotests as fuel stations run dry
OL,6,FOperations at the port, run by Irish
OL,7,FRail, have been affected by a blockade
OL,8,Fof fuel protesters in the nearby town
OL,9,Fof Kilrane, Co Wexford.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Irish Rail said the
OL,12,Fport will soon be at capacity and will
OL,13,Fnot be able to take in any more
OL,14,Ffreight ` resulting in ships having to
OL,15,Fwait on anchor or be diverted to
OL,16,Fanother port if possible.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, ministers said the Irish
OL,19,FDefence Forces are "on standby" to
OL,20,Fhelp gardai remove blockades at
OL,21,Fcritical infrastructure.
OL,26,@{D@TOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
