OL,3,CFurther motorway closures due to
OL,4,Cprotests as fuel stations run dry
OL,6,FBlockades have resulted in full
OL,7,Fclosures of parts of the M50 ring road
OL,8,Faround Dublin, as well as the M4, M6,
OL,9,FM7, M8, M9 and M20.
OL,11,FTransport Infrastructure Ireland,
OL,12,Fwhich is responsible for motorways,
OL,13,Fsaid there is "significant disruption"
OL,14,Fto its network impacting counties
OL,15,FClare, Limerick, Tipperary, Laois,
OL,16,FOffaly, Kildare, Galway, Cork, and
OL,17,FDublin.
OL,19,FIt said it was working closely with
OL,20,Fgardai in managing traffic
OL,21,Fdistribution.
OL,26,@uD@OOUuD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
