PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775981091
OL,3,CFurther motorway closures due to
OL,4,Cprotests as fuel stations run dry
OL,6,FThe protests, which have also seen
OL,7,Fslow-moving convoys and outright
OL,8,Fstoppages on major motorways as well
OL,9,Fas a blockade on Dublin city's main
OL,10,Fthoroughfare, began on Tuesday over
OL,11,Fthe cost of fuel.
OL,13,FParticipants include professional
OL,14,Fdrivers, farmers and hauliers as well
OL,15,Fas taxi and bus operators.
OL,17,FMany official representative groups
OL,18,Frecognised by Government have
OL,19,Fexpressed sympathy with the cause but
OL,20,Fhave said they have not been involved
OL,21,Fin organising the protests.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775981091
OL,3,CFurther motorway closures due to
OL,4,Cprotests as fuel stations run dry
OL,6,FGovernment ministers engaged with some
OL,7,Fof these groups on Friday but a
OL,8,Fspokesman for the protesters expressed
OL,9,F"devastation" that they were excluded
OL,10,Ffrom the meeting.
OL,12,FA commitment from the coalition on
OL,13,FFriday night to deliver a
OL,14,F"substantial" package of measures on
OL,15,Ffuel costs was not enough to dissuade
OL,16,Fprotesters from continuing blockades.
OL,18,FChristopher Duffy, a spokesman for the
OL,19,Fgrouping in Dublin city centre, said
OL,20,Fthe protest would continue until there
OL,21,Fwas a "serious reduction in our costs".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@MO]vD@AOUvD@MO]}D@GOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
