OL,3,CFurther motorway closures due to
OL,4,Cprotests as fuel stations run dry
OL,6,FTalks between Government departments
OL,7,Fand representative bodies are set to
OL,8,Fcontinue at lunchtime on Saturday,
OL,9,Fwith a view to finalising what deputy
OL,10,Fpremier Simon Harris said would be
OL,11,F"substantial and significant" measures
OL,12,Ffor affected industries.
OL,14,FPolice in Northern Ireland said they
OL,15,Fwere "maintaining an ongoing
OL,16,Fassessment" in relation to social
OL,17,Fmedia posts calling for similar
OL,18,Fplanned protests there.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@]O]wD@FOUxD@KO]
